1. *Gazila* je stigla u stanicu. (The train arrived at the station.)
2. On je *govorio* o svojim planovima. (He was talking about his plans.)
3. On je *gazio* preko travnjaka. (He was walking across the lawn.)
4. *Gazimo* dalje! (Let's go further!)
5. Ona je *gledala* u nebo. (She was looking at the sky.)
6. *Gazile* su bile u pokretu. (The trains were in motion.)
7. On je *gutao* svoju čašu. (He was gulping down his glass.)
8. *Gaziti* taj put će biti rizično. (Travelling this road will be risky.)